-13T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"點解「更吹落」之後係頓號？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"問得好！我嘅睇法係咁：<br />\n因為古代其實無我哋今日嘅標點符號<br />\n所以當現代學者加返上去時，會捉返個語感<br />\n有人會喺呢個位用「，」，有人覺得「、」好<br />\n判斷語速、語意之別，短匆、短語並列，會多用「、」<br />\n不過標點係後世強加上去，所以會有好多唔同版本"},{"pid":"c96c192d38af367b7dd7e8ff051b25f5c94dd160","tid":2406974,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e775cd27f8d32223f1ccfe705898c61c32aac564","tid":2406974,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"553de95b85e714b17793387f8eb8265c9774c965","tid":2406974,"uid":17335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fae47dc3ab040a37d14a02371788729f479e9a4f","tid":2406974,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比大家情人節溝女溝仔用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"打開個連登朗誦呢篇文俾條女/仔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你post喺叫春台係唔會有人用到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5dabefdda804d9428542f82e4bd97b8946b7b1","tid":2406974,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e775cd27f8d32223f1ccfe705898c61c32aac564","tid":2406974,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"553de95b85e714b17793387f8eb8265c9774c965","tid":2406974,"uid":17335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fae47dc3ab040a37d14a02371788729f479e9a4f","tid":2406974,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比大家情人節溝女溝仔用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"打開個連登朗誦呢篇文俾條女/仔聽<img src=\"/as